GET info about SpaceX missions

Source: R/get_SpaceX_ships.R
get_SpaceX_ships.Rd

GET info about SpaceX missions

get_SpaceX_ships(...)

Arguments

...

: Query string to API. See more in details.

Value

data.frame with parsed data from SpaceX API.

Examples


# get all SpaceX ships
get_SpaceX_ships()
